      "kind": "word",
      "cefrLevel": "null",
      "senses": [
        {
          "pos": "noun",
          "definition": "an enzyme that accelerates the hydrolysis of prunasin, occurring in yeast and bitter almonds, involved in amygdalin breakdown.",
